9015 Feature_HasMips32Bit = 13,

9017 Feature_HasMips32r5Bit = 15,
9018 Feature_HasMips32r6Bit = 16,

9020 Feature_IsGP64bitBit = 33,
9021 Feature_IsGP32bitBit = 32,

9023 Feature_IsPTR32bitBit = 36,

12386 const FeatureBitset &RequiredFeatures = FeatureBitsets[RequiredFeaturesRefs[Inst.getOpcode()]];
12387 FeatureBitset MissingFeatures =
12388 (AvailableFeatures & RequiredFeatures) ^
12389 RequiredFeatures;
12390 if (MissingFeatures.any()) {
12391 std::ostringstream Msg;
12392 Msg << "Attempting to emit " << MCII.getName(Inst.getOpcode()).str()
12393 << " instruction but the ";
12394 for (unsigned i = 0, e = MissingFeatures.size(); i != e; ++i)
12395 if (MissingFeatures.test(i))
12396 Msg << SubtargetFeatureNames[i] << " ";
12397 Msg << "predicate(s) are not met";
12398 report_fatal_error(Msg.str());
12399 }
